        <item>
            <title>日本時興超 cheap 100 円袋仔當銀包，厚銀包已經落伍，專家: 電子支付少帶現金</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/japan-small-wallet/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japan-small-wallet</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/japan-small-wallet/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 11:16:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子支付]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294684</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>科技日新月異，消費習慣隨之變遷，錢包的使用風貌亦正悄然轉型。日本一項調查透露，小型錢包漸成潮流，年輕人尤愛輕巧實惠之選，如 100 日元的雜誌附贈品或三摺設計。東京原宿 3 Coins 推出的 550 日元（約港幣 29 元）錢包，以物美價廉之姿風靡市場，僅 1 個月內幾近售罄，僅餘黑色存貨，足見其魅力。更有甚者，100 円商店的塑膠收納袋搖身一變成為「錢包」，折射出世人對成本與實用的重新思量。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig143scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig143scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig143scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲東京原宿 3 Coins 推出的 550 日元錢包</p><h2>小型錢包何以乘勢而起</h2><p>「小廢包」盛行，錢包尺寸因勢利導縮減。不少人為搭配輕便手袋，精心挑選袖珍錢包，僅置卡片與少量現金，簡約中見巧思。智能手機支付普及，更令實體錢包退居幕後。渋谷 109 實驗室所長一語道破：數碼化洪流，如無現金交易與會員卡電子化，削弱錢包需求，「小廢包」遂乘風而上。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig320scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig320scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig320scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲節目調查指因為手袋尺寸較小，所以改用更小的錢包</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294688" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig13scre-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig13scre-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig13scre.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小廢包盛行</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig119scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig119scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig119scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家會特地選用更小的錢包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/xtf2865e168739605121-694x509.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="509" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/xtf2865e168739605121-694x509.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/xtf2865e168739605121.jpg 1026w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲渋谷 109 實驗室所長長田麻衣表示因為電子支付盛行，現代人較少用現金，所以銀包尺寸相應縮細</p><h2>「#100 均財布界隈」異軍突起</h2><p>社交媒體上「#100 均財布界隈」聲勢浩大，意思是使用 100 円店的小型收納袋代替錢包。渋谷街頭一位 16 歲少女表示因屢失錢包，她轉投卡通塑膠袋，經濟實惠且無後顧之憂。另一名受訪 50 歲市民則讚透明薄身設計一目瞭然，低調中不失實用。東京 100 円店員工笑言，小型收納袋去年起銷量節節上升，顧客別出心裁的用法教店方喜出望外。日本《朝日新聞》2024 年報導亦指出，100 円商店錢包銷量持續攀升，彰顯實用與價格並重的消費傾向。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig26scre-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig26scre-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig26scre.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「#100 均財布界隈」意思是使用百元商店的透明收納袋充當銀包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294697" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig238scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig238scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig238scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲受訪少女表示自己經常丟失銀包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig531scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig531scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig531scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲已經丟失過 3 次</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294696" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig229scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig229scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig229scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲因此使用用百元商店的透明收納袋充當銀包</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig255scr-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig255scr-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/100ntbsnewsdig255scr.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲東京 100 円店員工表示沒有想過收納袋可以當銀包用</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
